These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, soy-milk, sprite, tea
City: miami, berlin, london, rome, new-york
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, september, december, august, may
There are 5 different nationalities: british, indonesian, nigerian, spanish, turkish
 1. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
 2. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the indonesian##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 8. the turkish is in an even position##4
 9. the british is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
10. the person who's birthday is in december is the person traveling to london##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
12. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
13. the person drinking tea is on the right of the indonesian##1
14. the turkish is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
15. the person who's birthday is in august is the person drinking sprite##1
16. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |        2        |     3      |    4     |     5     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk    | hot-chocolate   | sprite     | tea      | milk      |
| City           | london | new-york | miami    | rome | berlin |
| Birthday   | december       | july         | august      | september      | may    |
| Nationality   | nigerian    | spanish         | indonesian | turkish  | british   |

