.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, cooking, drawing, photography, woodworking
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: aconite, orchid, balloon-flower, amaryllis, poppy
There are 5 different favourite colors: orange, blood-red, pink, azure, lilac
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, bus, quad-bike, roller, snowmobile
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who growspoppy##1
 4. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 5. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person driving the boat##2
 9. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
10. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
11. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
13. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
14. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |      5      |
| Hobby         | photography | cooking | drawing   | card-games | woodworking |
