City: venice, hannover, new-york, boston, miami
The people have 5 different jobs:  writer, musician, dancer, security-guard, pilot
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 7. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1
 8. the dancer is on the left or right of the pilot##3
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is the dancer##1
10. the person drinking coffee is the person traveling to hannover##1
11. the security-guard is the person drinking milk##1
12. the person traveling to hannover is between the musician and the person watching action movies##2
13. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
14. the person traveling to miami is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
16. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |      4       |       5       |
